SELECT c."Id", c."CategoryName", c."CreatedBy", p."Id", p."AddedAt", p."AddedBy", p."CategoryId", p."Description", p."InventoryId", p."Name", p."Price", p."Status"
FROM "Categories" AS c

SELECT c."Id", c."CategoryName", c."CreatedBy", p."Id", p."AddedAt", p."AddedBy", p."CategoryId", p."Description", p."InventoryId", p."Name", p."Price", p."Status"
FROM "Categories" AS c
